languages.text: {n}Джай искоса смотрит на вас с печальной улыбкой.{/n} "Кое в чем я не врала тебе никогда, {name}".
{n}Jae slants a look at you, smiling sadly.{/n} "There are some things I've never lied to you about, {name}."

languages.text: {n}婕伊斜着眼看了你一眼，露出了悲伤的笑意。{/n}“有些事情我从来没对你说过谎，{name}。”
languages.original_text: {n}Jae slants a look at you, smiling sadly.{/n} "There are some things I've never lied to you about, {name}."

languages.text: {n}Jae te lanza una mirada de soslayo y una sonrisa triste.{/n} «Hay cosas sobre las que nunca le he mentido, {name}».
